  dialogueSteps:
  - line: "Good anticipation. Junctions aren\u2019t just about rules \u2014 they\u2019re
      about reading other drivers."
    stepType: 0
    correctOptionIndex: 0
    feedbackCorrect: 
    feedbackWrong: 
    buttonTexts: []
  - line: "Before we continue, let's see if you were paying attention in the previous
      scene. Tell me \u2014 what\u2019s the speed limit on this road?"
    stepType: 1
    correctOptionIndex: 1
    feedbackCorrect: "Correct. The speed limit here is 50 km/h. Always stay alert
      for posted limits \u2014 they can change quickly."
    feedbackWrong: Not quite. Check the posted signs carefully It is 50km/h, mentioned
      right as we were coming into the junction.
    buttonTexts:
    - 30 km/h
    - 50 km/h
    - 60 km/h
    - 80 km/h
  - line: "Alright, now let\u2019s continue and turn right at this T-junction."
    stepType: 0
    correctOptionIndex: 0
    feedbackCorrect: 
    feedbackWrong: 
