  - line: "Alright, we\u2019re on our way to join the motorway now. Take a look at
      this sign coming up \u2014 what does it indicate?"
    stepType: 3
    correctOptionIndex: 0
    correctOptionIndexes: 
    partialCorrectFeedback: 
