      - Stop sign ahead
      - No entry
      - Roundabout ahead
      correctOptionIndex: 3
      correctFeedback: "That\u2019s right. This sign warns you that there\u2019s
        a roundabout ahead. As we\u2019re heading towards the motorway, you should
        start slowing down and prepare to give way to traffic already on the roundabout."
      wrongFeedback: "Not quite. This is a roundabout warning sign. Since we\u2019re
